A man who impersonated a Kenya Defence Forces officer has been sentenced to three years in jail after he was found guilty by a Nakuru court. Alex Odhiambo Nungo presented himself to Pauline Mokeira as a KDF officer with intent to defraud her in Race Course, Nakuru. ALSO READ:

